import React from 'react' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' const OrderTableBody = ({dataState}) => { return ( {dataState?.map((data, i) => (
{data.paymentIntent.id} {new Date(data.createdAt).toLocaleString('en-US', { month: 'long', day: '2-digit', year: 'numeric' })}{' '} {new Date(data.createdAt).toLocaleString('en-US', { hour: 'numeric', minute: 'numeric', hour12: true })}
{data.paymentIntent.status}
{data.paymentIntent.amount ? `₹${data.paymentIntent.amount}` : '₹0.00'} {data.paymentIntent.method === 'cod' ? 'Cash on Delivery' : 'Online Payment'}
{data.orderStatus}
))} ) } export default OrderTableBody
